g.text: primary workflow for creating and modifying
quantum circuits within the composer environment
place quantum gate on circuit canvas at specified position,
insert into DAG structure and push overlapping gates forward
modify gate configuration including type, parameters,
target qubits, and control qubit assignments
reposition gate on canvas to new qubit placement,
combine multiple gates into composite circuit element,
register new composite gate in gates panel for reuse
decompose composite circuit back into constituent gates,
restore individual gates to circuit canvas layout
load OpenQASM code file, parse syntax,
convert to circuit representation and render on canvas
automatically synchronize circuit state to backend storage,
